OL,3,CInfant CPR: Mum launches campaign
OL,4,Cfollowing death of her 14-day-old baby
OL,6,FA woman from Derby who lost her baby
OL,7,Fboy when he was just 14 days old has
OL,8,Ffeatured in a new video highlighting
OL,9,Fthe importance of knowing how to
OL,10,Fperform infant CPR ` saying the
OL,11,Flessons from it could have saved his
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,FRachel Pepper's son Rowan stopped
OL,15,Fbreathing at their home in October
OL,16,F2022.
OL,18,FRowan died in hospital just days later
OL,19,Ffrom Sudden Infant Death Syndrome
OL,20,F(also known as cot death) ` just two
OL,21,Fweeks after he was born.
