OL,3,CInfant CPR: Mum launches campaign
OL,4,Cfollowing death of her 14-day-old baby
OL,6,FRachel and her partner Christian have
OL,7,Fsince started a campaign in his memory
OL,8,Fcalled "Rowan's Rule", which aims to
OL,9,Fraise awareness of how to perform
OL,10,Finfant CPR should anyone need it.
OL,12,FThe couple say they want to raise
OL,13,Fawareness both locally and nationally,
OL,14,Fso no parent has to go through what
OL,15,Fthey had to.
OL,17,F"I sincerely hope you never have to
OL,18,Fuse the information in this film"
