OL,3,CInfant CPR: Mum launches campaign
OL,4,Cfollowing death of her 14-day-old baby
OL,6,FThe film, created by the University of
OL,7,FHospitals Derby and Burton NHS Trust,
OL,8,Fcontains important step-by-step
OL,9,Finstructions on what to do should you
OL,10,Fsee a baby not breathing or in urgent
OL,11,Fneed of CPR.
OL,13,FRachel starts the film by saying: "The
OL,14,Finformation you're about to learn in
OL,15,Fthis film could have saved my son's
OL,16,Flife...I sincerely hope you never have
OL,17,Fto use the information in this film."
