OL,6,FShe added: "We are over the moon (the
OL,7,Flocal hospital trust is implementing
OL,8,Fthe film). I think it is the right
OL,9,Fthing to do. They will be showing it
OL,10,Fin antenatal rooms ` they have shown
OL,11,Ffantastic support.
OL,13,F"We now want to get it out there to
OL,14,Fother hospital trusts so they can
OL,15,Fshare the same message. There's been
OL,16,Finterest. It's had around 15,000 views
OL,17,Fin around a fortnight.
