OL,3,CInfant CPR: Mum launches campaign
OL,4,Cfollowing death of her 14-day-old baby
OL,6,F"All we want is to tell people what to
OL,7,Fdo. We are not saying it will save
OL,8,Fpeople's lives but hopefully it will.
OL,9,FHopefully people will not have to use
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,F"I remember not knowing what to do (to
OL,13,Fhelp Rowan) and that will always stay
OL,14,Fwith me. That is something we will
OL,15,Fnever get away from. This film I hope
OL,16,Fwill avoid that feeling of
OL,17,Fhelplessness and not knowing what to
OL,18,Fdo."
