OL,3,CInfant CPR: Mum launches campaign
OL,4,Cfollowing death of her 14-day-old baby
OL,6,FThe University Hospitals of Derby and
OL,7,FBurton Trust (UHDB) say the video will
OL,8,Fbe shared "with women, birthing people
OL,9,Fand families who access our services".
OL,11,FThe Trust said that while many people
OL,12,Fknow how to perform CPR on adults,
OL,13,F"there is less awareness about CPR for
OL,14,Finfants and children".
OL,16,FIt added: "National guidance for post-
OL,17,Fnatal care does not currently include
OL,18,Foffering basic training for infant
OL,19,FCPR".
